729504f-b.title: Richmond: Richmond Terrace - John Street
729504f-b.text:
2380 Richmond Terrace, adjoining the S.E. corner of John Street, showing Captain George Housman's house. Captain
Housman was a rich oysterman.
March, 1924
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same, another view.
September 28, 1924
By Wn. T. Davis thmwugh P. L. Sperr
